{"tid":330980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警疑濫權溝女】男警查ID「抄牌」 凌晨WhatsApp問有冇男友","createTime":"2017-07-21T17:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T10:18:47.000Z","uid":23479,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46ae1c14f262301546bd9244a06543cb8194aefd","tid":330980,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"「例如又問跟男朋友一起多久，你這麽漂亮也去機鋪打機等問題，都令到我女友感到尷尬。」不願上鏡讀大學的Alan，其女友Candy早前在遊戲機中心被警員「抄牌」(索取電話號碼)，說方便了解機鋪事情。怎知那名警員當晚凌晨傳來訊息，竟然讚她漂亮，問她有沒有男朋友等私人問題，十分離譜。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAlan說當時他不在場，「7月18日時，下午5時45分，我女朋友跟數名朋友，共五人，在那裡（荃灣南豐中心三樓一間遊戲機中心）打機。當時有數名便衣警員入來查身分證。她們數人都被要求查身分證。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n查完後怎樣？「(之後)有名警員給回他她們身分證，另一名警員就問她們其中三人，取了電話號碼。他說近日放假多人來打機，擔心有特別事發生，必要時致電她們，查問是否知情等。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n其後，那名警員果然很「勤力」，「那天(19號)凌晨二時多，我女朋友已睡覺，收到WhatsApp訊息。內容是你知我是誰嗎？我是昨天查身分證的警員。」Alan說，由於女友已睡了，翌日早上才回覆訊息。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n那名警員問了什麼？「大慨是問比較詳細的住址和職業等。由一些個人問題開始入手，之後好像變成聊天似的。」之後越問越不對勁，「之後那警員又說，多口問句，你有沒有男朋友呀？都是一些私人的問題。例如又問跟男朋友一起多久，你這麽漂亮也去機鋪打機等問題，都令到我女友感到尷尬。」是查案還是「溝女」，你懂的。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAlan覺得那名警員做法不妥，十九日在討論區開帖子，問網民意見，「我覺得都應該上討論區問問意見，警察這樣做是否違規。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n出帖子後，該警員有否再找你女友？「那天再沒收到WhatsApp，我女友亦沒再回覆他。但到了20號早上9時多，她收到兩個沒來電顯示的電話。她沒有接，我叫她不要接。到(20號)傍晚七時，她再接到沒來電顯示電話。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n而Alan根據電話號碼，追查到該名男警的Facebook，照片是同一人。根據網頁顯示，該名男警姓葉。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_532180_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_532180_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&d=CKgDxfPOCJFUynQvfp2Tj9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5903efa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_532180_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&h=69229022\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_532180_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine</a>"},{"pid":"2246f3147b129faa22db433598bf6e9980534f6c","tid":330980,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4609d585431b6a436063e74318e022dd6cff66e2","tid":330980,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"真心希望男警有老婆仔女"},{"pid":"73bcbf5ab1150b06ce558164416a81906f739403","tid":330980,"uid":87780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:18:57.000Z","msg":"偽進仔想溝大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cfd8518322c7a16b2b4021718c9b0ada4b497d","tid":330980,"uid":43173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"攞上警署報性騷擾已收皮"},{"pid":"e02fb22a8cdcfddf3769d90892bc7f2e3eeb7584","tid":330980,"uid":93217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"搞大佢，hoball<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b850b2d8b8360f2a11b289f7bebfb96859e512c1","tid":330980,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:17:34.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11550930a5f3d4564feaf03f942b346122c52716","tid":330980,"uid":72801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5b142a6a6ecddd7a268ac7d8ca37b92ac986d6","tid":330980,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"仲唔佈驚等幾時"},{"pid":"b1ff8c514b27daaf4055a77819d0b3cdda78a57c","tid":330980,"uid":80593,"like":4,"dislike":1